    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "healing? i dont know if that's even what this is. it doesn't feel like grief... it feels more like just being done. like the life part of me is gone and there's nothing left to \"heal\" in an empty house. it just feels exhausting, pretending to be a person when i'm just the leftovers of who i was supposed to be.",
